situation at Ferragamo ( https://puck.news/newsletter_content/nikes-regress=
ion-marc-jacobs-show-notes-a-retail-tariff-guide/?utm_campaign=3DLine+Sheet=
+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282=
%2F7%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3D=
f6c60617da42abd12a ), which fired its C.E.O. on Monday: =E2=80=9COMG, Ferra=
gamo is going to hell in a derivative-old-lady-looking handbasket. That bra=
nd is a mess, and it=E2=80=99s sooo sad. I agree that a lot of the items ar=
e really really good! But the collection is all over the place, and the pre=
sentation of it in
campaigns, and particularly in the stores, is just much, much too punchy an=
d feels way too try-hard.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A designer=C2=A0

=C2=A0

On Est=C3=A9e Lauder Co.=E2=80=99s current strat ( https://puck.news/estee-=
lauder-needs-to-change-a-new-ceo-is-not-enough/?utm_campaign=3DLine+Sheet+-=
+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2=
F7%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6=
c60617da42abd12a ): =E2=80=9CI have to say the situation at ELC is very con=
fusing right now. My biggest question is
whether the board is in a better place to guide these changes. I know their=
 board has been a mess for a while, but Paul J. Fribourg stepping up to buy=
 $25 million seemed notable and even the new C.F.O. bought... whereas nobod=
y from management of the board had bought stock since the GFC.=E2=80=9D =E2=
=80=94An investor

On the Sabato exit ( https://puck.news/say-it-aint-sabato-de-sarno/?utm_cam=
paign=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+=
-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcusto=
mer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ): =E2=80=9CAs a finance guy who is
particularly fond of Gucci loafers (I have probably 20 pairs), I am hopeful=
 that the next steward returns to the styles seen under Frida Giannini=E2=
=80=99s leadership. The latest =E2=80=981953=E2=80=99 is a cheap (but expen=
sive!) imitation of the far superior older shoe; the primary 1953 is lined =
in cheap canvas that makes it challenging to wear sockless. My favorite pai=
rs are those from the early 2010s, with the slightly taller heel that retai=
led for a modest $545 in period. I have spent far more than
that resoling those pairs again and again.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A finance guy =
who=E2=80=99s probably fun at parties=C2=A0

=C2=A0

On the brilliance of Marc Jacobs ( https://puck.news/newsletter_content/nik=
es-regression-marc-jacobs-show-notes-a-retail-tariff-guide/?utm_campaign=3D=
Line+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_content=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCR=
IBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&utm_source=3Dcustomer.io&u=
tm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a ): =E2=80=9CNo one has delivered creativity at=
 Louis Vuitton the way Marc Jacobs
did, and it=E2=80=99s the reason they are having such success with the rela=
unch of the Murakami collaboration. They are smartly resurrecting what real=
ly worked. Marc understands how to evolve with the current cultural convers=
ation and make it into compelling product.=E2=80=9D=E2=80=94A consultant

=C2=A0

On Lauren=E2=80=99s Vuori ( https://puck.news/the-vuori-reality-distortion-=
complex/?utm_campaign=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_conte=
nt=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_medium=3Demail_action&ut=
m_source=3Dcustomer.io&utm_term=3Df6c60617da42abd12a )
obsession: =E2=80=9CFascinated by your fascination with Vuori. I have to as=
k=E2=80=94as a mom in Coral Gables typing this while wearing Splits59 leggi=
ngs and an Alo ribbed T=E2=80=94are you sponsored by Vuori? As someone who =
has tried to =E2=80=98get dressed=E2=80=99 but can=E2=80=99t muster the ene=
rgy to leave my favorite activewear, I follow this space doggedly! I have a=
n aversion to Vuori, but feel the walls closing in! Am I missing something?=
=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A reader who might enjoy Lauren=E2=80=99s analysis of Vu=
ori=E2=80=99s success on her
Fashion People ( https://podcasts.apple.com/us/podcast/fashion-people/id174=
1589082?utm_campaign=3DLine+Sheet+-+SUBSCRIBERS+%282%2F7%2F25%29&utm_conten=
